Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大家请注意\N{\fs14}Can I get everyone's attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉先生 请举手\N{\fs14}Mr. Williams please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位是威廉先生 请您举手示意一下好吗\N{\fs14}Please raise your right hand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否能够郑重起誓\N{\fs14}Do you solemnly swear that the testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你将要陈述的事情 是千真万确\N{\fs14}you're about to give is the truth, the whole truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不带半点虚言的吗\N{\fs14}and nothing but the truth, so help you God?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 先生 - 谢谢您\N{\fs14}Yes, sir. Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那么请坐吧\N{\fs14}Please, be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉先生 你能尽你所能给我们再现\N{\fs14}Mr. Williams, can you please give us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,深水地平线钻井平台事故发生的经过吗\N{\fs14}your best recollection of the event\N{\fs14}on the Deepwater Horizon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,大概晚上九点半的时候 我正在和我的妻子通话\N{\fs14}I was on the phone around 9:30 with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,突然听到"嘶嘶嘶"的声音\N{\fs14}That's when I heard the hissing noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,紧接着便听到了引擎旋转的声音\N{\fs14}I hear the engines start to rev.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"嘶嘶嘶"的声音也演变为洪水的咆哮声\N{\fs14}The hissing turned into a full-blown roar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,声音巨大到无法言喻\N{\fs14}Higher than I can even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,顷刻间又发生了一场爆炸\N{\fs14}And within seconds, there was a huge explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,热浪从四面八方袭来 温度高到无法忍受\N{\fs14}Projectiles comin ' from everywhere. The heat was overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,您能给我描述一下\N{\fs14}Can you please explain to me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,深水地平线的报警系统是如何设置的吗\N{\fs14}how the Deepwater Horizon's alarm system is set up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,常规报警功能是已经设置好的\N{\fs14}The general alarm is set up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用来预警可能存在的危险因素 最有可能的是火灾\N{\fs14}to inform the entire rig of, number one, fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,其次 可燃气体 第三 有毒气体\N{\fs14}number two, combustible gas, number three, toxic gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不同意外发生时 报警系统会发出不同的警报声 同时发出不同的光\N{\fs14}Each condition has a distinct tone and a distinct visual light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在四月二十日的晚上\N{\fs14}On the evening of April 20th did you hear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,您有听到过什么警报声吗\N{\fs14}any one of those alarms\N{\fs14}on the Deepwater Horizon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 先生\N{\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那您知道警报为什么没响吗 先生\N{\fs14}Do you know why you never heard that alarm, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉先生\N{\fs14}Mr. Williams?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉先生\N{\fs14}Mr. Williams!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,深度已达三千英尺\N{\fs14}Passing through 3,000 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,继续下潜\N{\fs14}Continuing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,目前已经触到北侧\N{\fs14}Gonna stick to the north side of this so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,扫描\N{\fs14}Scan on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩约五百英尺\N{\fs14}'Bout 500 foot of riser left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,防喷器可见\N{\fs14}BOP's in view.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,井口是什么样子\N{\fs14}How's that wellhead surface looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,轻微腐蚀\N{\fs14}Minor corrosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,程度和我想象的差不多\N{\fs14}Not much more than I'd expect on wellhead of this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 标记一下 把它吊上来\N{\fs14}All right, mark it. Bring her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚做了一个超级可怕的梦\N{\fs14}I just had the craziest dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fs14}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 我也在你的梦里吗\N{\fs14}Wow? Was I in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我 没有\N{\fs14}I was... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我在参加一场音乐会 然后在舞台的边缘\N{\fs14}I was at a concert and then on the side of the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那里\N{\fs14}there was this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有一只 只有两条腿的兔子\N{\fs14}It was like a two-legged rabbit and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不出来你这个梦有什么吓人的\N{\fs14}I don't know what part of that is more terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 听我说\N{\fs14}Listen to me. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我一动\N{\fs14}I would move...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那只兔子就会模仿我做同样的动作\N{\fs14}And then it would mimic everything I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 别再说了 因为我知道这是发生在什么地方的事情\N{\fs14}Oh, don't tell me anymore, because I know where this is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得那只兔子是我的 - 母亲 嗯 知道了\N{\fs14}- I think the rabbit was my... mother. - Mother. Yes. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 现在这成了我的噩梦了\N{\fs14}Thank you. Now it's my nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,它充满了敌意 - 好了\N{\fs14}It was hostile.- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,它是只充满敌意的兔子 - 嗯\N{\fs14}It was a hostile rabbit.- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了\N{\fs14}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么\N{\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吗\N{\fs14}That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,未来21个日夜你就打算这样丢下我\N{\fs14}That's how you're gonna leave me for 21 days and nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想让你再睡会儿\N{\fs14}I'm lettin' you get your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我更需要除了睡觉之外的其它东西\N{\fs14}Well, I need many other things than sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你得保证不要把你母亲也扯进来\N{\fs14}You have to promise not to bring up your mother, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fs14}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你是想要三十还是六十 还是九十秒的爱情大礼包\N{\fs14}So you want the 30, the 60, or the 90-second love package?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 我当然想要最大的 九十秒\N{\fs14}Honey, I'm gonna take the whole 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 压力好大\N{\fs14}Oh, the pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,压力 压力 压力\N{\fs14}The pressure, the pressure, the pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想念你的笑脸\N{\fs14}Gonna miss that laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想念你的红唇 - 啊\N{\fs14}Gonna miss that mouth. - Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\fs14}Give me those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你\N{\fs14}Love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这样 伙计\N{\fs14}This is not our deal, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好 真不错\N{\fs14}All right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你太高估你的技术了 还自以为能赶得上机修工人\N{\fs14}You consistently overestimate your skills as a mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 宝贝儿\N{\fs14}Let's go, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我来开车吧 - 不好\N{\fs14}- Let me drive.- Mmm-mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我来开 - 不行\N{\fs14}- Let me drive! - Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我来 - 不行\N{\fs14}- Let me drive.- Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fs14}Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的想开吗 - 是的\N{\fs14}- Really wanna drive? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那你得先把你那破车卖了 再买辆杜卡迪\N{\fs14}Then sell that piece of shit and get a Ducati.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,大声点 莽撞的家伙\N{\fs14}Loud. Bull in a china shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷\N{\fs14}Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我没敲门就进来了 因为我想要个弟弟\N{\fs14}I only did not knock because I want a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好 很好 你够让人操心的\N{\fs14}Okay. Well, that's disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你不应该知道这种少儿不宜的东西\N{\fs14}'Cause you're not supposed to know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你只应该知道小孩子很可爱 仅此而已\N{\fs14}You're supposed to just think babies are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大声点 - 你能给我坐好吗 啊\N{\fs14}- Loud. - Will you sit down, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的想要个弟弟\N{\fs14}I really want a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗 - - 好得很\N{\fs14}- How's it goin'? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 来 给爸爸看看\N{\fs14}Honey, show Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还没完 - 你做得真好\N{\fs14}- I'm not done. - You did such a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是该表现的时候了\N{\fs14}It's showtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太棒了\N{\fs14}It's really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你别这样看着我 - 为什么\N{\fs14}- You can't look at me.- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你看得我浑身不自在\N{\fs14}Because it makes me uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我看着你让你浑身不自在了\N{\fs14}My looking at you makes you uncomfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 停 - 好吧\N{\fs14}- Stop! - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的爸爸叫迈克\N{\fs14}My dad is Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他在石油钻探队工作 专门负责从海底钻出石油\N{\fs14}He works on a drilling rig that pumps oil out from underneath the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不 说错了 深水地平线从来不会从海里抽一滴石油 知道了吗 宝贝儿\N{\fs14}No, no, the Deepwater doesn't pump a drop of oil, okay, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是探险家\N{\fs14}We're the explorers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我爸爸和他的队友们发现了石油\N{\fs14}So my dad and his friends find the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后架上管道 好让剩下那些废物队友也来分一杯羹\N{\fs14}And then put in all the plumbing so other lamer crews can come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要说"废物"这个词 - 他们就是废物\N{\fs14}- Don't say "lamer.  - They are lamer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 但是听着 就算他们是\N{\fs14}Okay, but listen, even those lamer dudes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那他们也没想钻出任何东西 记住了\N{\fs14}they don't have to pump anything, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因为石油会自己冒出来的\N{\fs14}Because that oil wants to come rushing up naturally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 不 不 嘘 - 好 好\N{\fs14}- No, no, no, shh! - All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为石油 是个大怪兽\N{\fs14}Because that oil is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是古时候的恐龙变成的\N{\fs14}Like the mean old dinosaurs all that oil used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,三亿年来 这些古老的恐龙\N{\fs14}So for 300 million years, these old dinosaurs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,被挤压得越来越紧 越来越紧\N{\fs14}have been getting squeezed tighter and tighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道了 我们知道了 你用了两个"紧"字\N{\fs14}We get it. We get it. Just use two "tighters."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它们被压在深不可测的土壤和海洋之下\N{\fs14}'Cause they got miles of earth and ocean pressing down on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,它们被永远困住了 愤怒却无奈\N{\fs14}They're trapped. Ornery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸和他们队友在他们的头顶上钻了个洞\N{\fs14}Then Dad and his friends make a hole in their roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,耶\N{\fs14}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这些凶残的恐龙简直不敢相信自己的眼睛\N{\fs14}And these mean old dinosaurs can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们争相地想从这个洞涌出 然后 猛然地\N{\fs14}So they rush to the new hole. Then, smack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸和队友们安放了一个巨大的\N{\fs14}They run into a big machine that he and his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大机器 名叫 巨无霸\N{\fs14}have down on the ocean floor called a Big Guy Preventer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是防喷器\N{\fs14}Blowout Preventer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们插下一根管子\N{\fs14}They run into this stuff called mud...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 插进去 - 然后往里面注入大量的泥浆\N{\fs14}- All right, get it in there. - ...that they cram down the straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,泥浆又厚又重 所以可以阻止怪兽从下面涌出来\N{\fs14}The mud's so thick and heavy it blocks the monsters from coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们又赶往下一个目的地\N{\fs14}And then they sail away to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候那些废物们就开始炫耀 好像他们帮上了什么忙似的\N{\fs14}That's when all the lame-os show up all happy like they did something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说这个词\N{\fs14}Don't say "lame-o."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但明明是我爸爸降服恐龙的\N{\fs14}But it was my daddy who tamed the dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 耶  - 耶\N{\fs14}- Yeah!  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了 你要是永远都长不大该多好\N{\fs14}That was amazing. Stay ten forever, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你得送我化石\N{\fs14}Daddy, you need to get me a fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 好啊 - 我会的\N{\fs14}- Oh, yes. - I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把它举起来然后告诉全世界 是我爸爸驯服了恐龙\N{\fs14}I wanna be able to hold it up and say, "My daddy tames the dinosaurs."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉爸爸 玛姬的爸爸是怎么做的\N{\fs14}Tell Daddy what Maggie's dad did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她爸爸在动物园工作 然后送了她一只真的企鹅\N{\fs14}Her dad works at the zoo. And he brought a real penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你不能提这种要求 - 带回来一只企鹅\N{\fs14}- You can't do that! - Brought in a penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能拿这和企鹅比\N{\fs14}How do you compete with a penguin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你应该带回来化石 - 这有违自然规律\N{\fs14}- You get a fossil. - There should be rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 宝贝儿 - 怎么了\N{\fs14}- Honey! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这罐子怎么这么满 - 好了 快让它停下 停下\N{\fs14}- There's only so much stuff in the can! - Well, stop it! Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,加满汽油开车去上班 然后又加满汽油回去继续上班\N{\fs14}Buy gas to go to work to buy gas to go back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了能加更多的汽油好去上班\N{\fs14}To buy more gas to get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你知道账户密码 对吗\N{\fs14}Hey, you know the passwords, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道保险材料在哪吧 你知道 需要的时候要先找舒曼\N{\fs14}Where the insurance stuff is. You know, call Schuman first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在瞎说些什么啊 - 我只是\N{\fs14}- What are you talking about? - I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你到底想说什么 - 我只是\N{\fs14}- What are you on about? - I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是对上次坐救援直升机回来的经历心有余悸 那不\N{\fs14}I just got a little spooked on the go-home chopper last hitch. It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,给我来点\N{\fs14}Gimme some of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你最应该担心一个海员的时候\N{\fs14}Babe, the only time you start worrying about a Marine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他不发牢骚的时候\N{\fs14}is when he stops bitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别学我说话 - 我就学你了\N{\fs14}- Don't use my lines against me. - I'm using your line against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别学我 - 我就学了\N{\fs14}- Don't use my lines. - I just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了宝贝儿 - 好了\N{\fs14}- All right, babe. - All right, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我爱你 - 我也爱你\N{\fs14}- I love you. - I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 三周后见 - 好 三周后\N{\fs14}- See ya in three weeks. - Okay. In three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你要乖乖的\N{\fs14}Behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\fs14}Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,早 吉米先生\N{\fs14}Good morning, Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 最近情况怎么样 萨拉 - 很好 你近来可好\N{\fs14}- How we doin', Sarah? - Good. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我很好 - 请把包放在\N{\fs14}- I'm good. - You can place your bags
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,行李秤上 然后站上来\N{\fs14}on the baggage scale and step on the feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的目的地是  - 老地方 深水地平线\N{\fs14}- Where you headed today?  - Same place. Deepwater Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的目的地是  - 深水地平线\N{\fs14}Where you flying out to?  - Deepwater Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 您的雇主是 - 越洋公司\N{\fs14}- And who you work for? - Transocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道你的体重吗\N{\fs14}Wanna know how much you weigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道我想 - 181\N{\fs14}- You know I do.- 181.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我告诉过你什么来着  - 好 你做得很好\N{\fs14}- What'd I tell ya?  - Yeah, you did good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 保持现状就好 - 好的\N{\fs14}- Keep it that way. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 去大厅稍坐一下 时间到了的话\N{\fs14}Alrighty. Have a seat in the lobby and we'll call you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们会叫你的 - 谢谢\N{\fs14}- when your flight's ready. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,西姆 先生\N{\fs14}Mr. Sims?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 奥布莱恩先生  - 我叫大卫 西姆\N{\fs14}- Mr. O'Bryan?  - David Sims.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是吉米 哈勒尔 是深水地平线的海上安装经理\N{\fs14}My name's Jimmy Harrell. Offshore lnstallation Manager on Deepwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 谢谢你今天带我们来这儿\N{\fs14}Buddy, thank you very much for taking us out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们也自顾不暇了 你本来没必要这样做的\N{\fs14}I know you guys are swamped and you didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不得不 听着 你介意把领带取下来吗\N{\fs14}No, I had to. Listen, you mind losing that tie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,介意\N{\fs14}I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说你的领带不好 而是它的颜色\N{\fs14}It's not the tie. It's... It's the color.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 紫色 - 呃 更像洋红吧\N{\fs14}- Purple? - Uh... More magenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\fs14}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在钻井架上 红色警报跟你领带的这个颜色很像\N{\fs14}Well, magenta alarm on an oil rig is as bad as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这让人不得不迷信洋红是种不吉利的颜色\N{\fs14}That's worthy of superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早 - 迈克 威廉\N{\fs14}- Good morning. - Mike Williams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的目的地是哪里 - 深水地平线\N{\fs14}- Where you headed today? - Deepwater Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你不上班的时候都干些什么\N{\fs14}What'd ya do on your downtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我就开始鼓捣这些飞机\N{\fs14}I started workin' on that airboat again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我通常都开到六百到一千二百马力\N{\fs14}I'm upping it from 600 horsepower to 1,200 horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我有点 呃 多亏了塞森尼奇推进器的支撑这些大家伙才能发挥作用\N{\fs14}And I got me a little, uh, Sensenich prop off that Super Cub.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你以为你是在开飞船\N{\fs14}- Trying to make it fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有 我只是想开得再快一点\N{\fs14}- No, I just wanna make it go faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,说得大声清楚一点\N{\fs14}Loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 所有人都登机了\N{\fs14}Roger. Got everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 博斯科 我已经标记了深水地平线的坐标\N{\fs14}Hey, Bosco, I got the Deepwater Horizon coordinates in the FMS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,492号 机尾无异常状况\N{\fs14}492, your tail is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,风平浪静 2-1号已部署 海拔2997米\N{\fs14}Wind is calm. 2-1 is in use. Altimeter 2997.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,巴黎指挥部 这里是布里斯托2号\N{\fs14}Paris Control, this is Bristow 2 Bravo Gulf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正赶往海上 预计四十五分钟后到达深水地平线\N{\fs14}We 're headin ' out into open ocean. ETA 45 minutes to Deepwater Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 布里斯托2号\N{\fs14}Copy that, Bristow 2 Bravo Gulf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在英国石油公司负责的是什么工作 西姆先生\N{\fs14}What is it you do at BP, Mr. Sims?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 负责收尾\N{\fs14}- Completions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 该死 我们继续 吉米\N{\fs14}- Oh, shit, here we go, Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 但是你知道 我们 我们有点落后了\N{\fs14}Well, as you know, we... We a little behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,四十三天 但是谁在意啊 不是吗\N{\fs14}Forty-three days. But who's countin', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克 你会把奖金花在什么地方\N{\fs14}What were you gonna do with your bonus, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 建一座泳池 你呢 - 修车\N{\fs14}- Dig a pool. You? - Fix my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们第一次遇到井塌的情况吧\N{\fs14}You do know the first well collapsed on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,光是把那价值连城的钻探管给弄出来就花了整整五天时间\N{\fs14}Took us five days just to pull a million-dollar drill pipe out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这能怪谁\N{\fs14}Whose fault was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要花这么大力气去修 你开的是什么车?\N{\fs14}What are you drivin' that needs that much work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 福特野马 - 流线型的\N{\fs14}- '69 Mustang. - Fastback?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 乙烯表层的 - 它出了什么问题\N{\fs14}- Vinyl top - What's up with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有点掉链子\N{\fs14}Today it was a rough idle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,排出的气闻起来像刚从油管里出来的一样汽油一样\N{\fs14}Made the exhaust smell like gas right out of the pump.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那你没启动它的时候也有这种味道吗\N{\fs14}You smell gas when it's not running?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 所以肯定不是油箱漏油的原因\N{\fs14}No. So it's not a leak in the tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 该死\N{\fs14}- Hey! - Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们 撞到鸟了\N{\fs14}That was a bird strike, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也不想说\N{\fs14}I ain't sayin' nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,深水地平线近在咫尺了\N{\fs14}Deepwater Horizon is only a mile out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会安全着陆的 我们会毫发无损地完成工作的\N{\fs14}We should be fine to land. We'll run a safety check there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 这么壮观的工程简直就像出自上帝之手\N{\fs14}Well, anything that big oughta be made by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太美了\N{\fs14}That's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你要知道 它没有支柱 没有任何东西的支撑\N{\fs14}And you know it's not on stilts. It's not a jack-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我知道 但我还是难以相信这是一艘船\N{\fs14}Yeah, I do, and I still can't believe that thing's a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这得感谢坐在这儿的这位\N{\fs14}Well, you can thank this very talented young lady
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,天赋异禀的姑娘\N{\fs14}right back here for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,班克斯顿的人在这儿搞什么\N{\fs14}What the hell's the Bankston doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谁叫他们来的\N{\fs14}Who gave that order?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,2号布拉沃海湾准备降落\N{\fs14}2 Bravo Gulf, permission to land,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,深水地平线\N{\fs14}Deepwater Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 2号布拉沃海湾\N{\fs14}Permission granted, 2 Bravo Gulf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 开始降落 - 收到\N{\fs14}- Beginning our descent. - Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎登船\N{\fs14}Welcome aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都好了吗\N{\fs14}You guys already done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该从何说起 吉米先生\N{\fs14}I don't know what to tell you, Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 你们都弄好了吗  - 我不知道该怎么跟你说 迈克\N{\fs14}- Hey, you guys finished?  - I don't know what to tell you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们得有个人去找维德林 - 什么 这就完了\N{\fs14}- Somebody's gotta talk to Vidrine. - What? Are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 斯基普 - 你好 先生\N{\fs14}- Hey, Skip. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,测井队已经走了\N{\fs14}Logging team is leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 斯伦贝榭的人已经走了 走了\N{\fs14}Yeah, Schlumberger's out. They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,据说他们打算进行水泥固井检测的\N{\fs14}Briefing said they're supposed to be testing that cement down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 已经检测完了吗 - 迈克 你最近还好吧\N{\fs14}- Is it already finished? - Mike, how you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 斯基普 我们来这儿这样就完了  - 你得去找维德林\N{\fs14}- Skip, are we done here?  - You gotta talk to Vidrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,维德林\N{\fs14}Vidrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他说什么 - 我听不清\N{\fs14}- What'd he say? - I can't hear him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,斯基普先生怎么说\N{\fs14}What did Mr. Skip say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们本来要进行水泥固井检测\N{\fs14}They were supposed to test to see whether the cement was holdin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但我猜他们可能根本没做这事\N{\fs14}I guess they left without doin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 等等 他们没有\N{\fs14}What? Hold up, they didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,英国石油公司的混蛋把斯伦贝榭的人送回去了\N{\fs14}Those BP sons of bitches sent the Schlumberger guys home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的 - 真的\N{\fs14}- Seriously? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,库赫塔 这些班克斯顿的人在这干什么\N{\fs14}Kuchta, why is the Bankston here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fs14}Good morning to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在这儿干什么\N{\fs14}What is the Bankston doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,早 皮特\N{\fs14}Morning, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,见到我是不是很高兴\N{\fs14}Happy to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,当然高兴 安德里亚\N{\fs14}I'm always happy to see you, Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 厕所在哪 威廉 - 写着"厕所"的那里\N{\fs14}- Where's the pisser, Williams? - Sign that says "toilet".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,斯基普向你提到过进行水泥固井测验的事情没有\N{\fs14}Skip say anything to you about runnin' a cement log?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他没给过我一个电话 - 我们赢了\N{\fs14}- He ain't call me. - We win the war here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在才终于发现\N{\fs14}and I'm just now findin' out about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我没办法知道他们\N{\fs14}'Cause I sure as hell don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,到底有没有时间做水泥固井测验\N{\fs14}how they'd have the time to do the cement test,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们已经走了\N{\fs14}'cause they're flyin' away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 吉米 我在开船 拜托\N{\fs14}Shit, Jimmy, I just drive the boat, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 正向测绘进行得如何 - 一切正常\N{\fs14}- How'd the positive test go? - Positive test went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正处于拆卸钻机模式\N{\fs14}We're in rig down mode
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拆卸钻机模式\N{\fs14}Rig down mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们现在速度多少 - 速度166\N{\fs14}- How we looking? - Sitting at 166.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,风速185 海面很平静 没问题\N{\fs14}Winds are at 185 and around five knots. Seas are calm. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,密切注意我们的视野范围 静观其变\N{\fs14}Holding great over our watch circle. Sitting right on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在和那个骑摩托车的小子约会么\N{\fs14}Are you still dating that itty bitty guy with the motorcycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,推进器情况如何\N{\fs14}Any issues with the thrusters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安德里拉 - 什么事\N{\fs14}- Andrea? - Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,和班克斯顿的兰德里队长联系一下\N{\fs14}Get on the radio to Captain Landry on Bankston
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他在干嘛而且问清楚为什么\N{\fs14}and see what he's doin' and why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得太对了 吉米先生\N{\fs14}You got it, Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,达蒙 班克斯顿 这里是深水地平线 完毕\N{\fs14}Damon Bankston, this is Deepwater Horizon, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,深水地平线 这里是达蒙 班克斯顿 请继续\N{\fs14}Deepwater Horizon, this is Damon Bankston. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,海上安装经理想知道您现在在做什么\N{\fs14}The OIM wants to know what you're doin' here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我们现在正从一个坑跳到了另一个坑\N{\fs14}Well, I hear we gettin' off this beast and movin' on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以说 这真操蛋\N{\fs14}You can call it a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们什么时候可以开始\N{\fs14}When are we supposed to be leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 他们告诉我已经可以\N{\fs14}Well, I'm told to be ready
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,注入钻井泥浆了\N{\fs14}to start taking on drilling mud about 1800.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fs14}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你们今早进行了正向压力测试\N{\fs14}I heard you had a positive pressure test this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜 他们想当然地觉得 反向测试也会一切正常\N{\fs14}I guess they assume the negative test is gonna run just as smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们让我准备进行下一步\N{\fs14}They told me to get ready to start moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- "他们"是谁 - 英国石油公司的人\N{\fs14}- Who's "they"? - BP company men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,维德林 卡鲁扎\N{\fs14}Vidrine, Kaluza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我在等待命令然后 帮你们解决泥浆的问题\N{\fs14}I don't know. I wait for the order and come pick up your mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么问题\N{\fs14}Any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没 就这些了\N{\fs14}Nope. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说维德林和卡鲁扎希望我们已经搞定这棘手的事情\N{\fs14}So BP company men Vidrine and/or Kaluza are hoping that we have tamed this bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,而且已经准备好注入钻探泥浆了\N{\fs14}and are ready to displace drilling mud 1800 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗 队长\N{\fs14}Is that correct, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对 早 吉米先生\N{\fs14}That is correct. Mornin', Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,突如其来\N{\fs14}All of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这样\N{\fs14}Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 队长\N{\fs14}Thank you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,电话不能用了 迈克\N{\fs14}And the goddamn phones still don't work, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 请吩咐 吉米先生 - 能帮我一个忙吗\N{\fs14}- Hey, I flew in with you, Mr. Jimmy. - Would you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你快去钻井棚\N{\fs14}- Run down to the drill shack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,问问杰森 斯伦贝榭的人有没有完成他们的工作\N{\fs14}Ask Jason if those Schlumberger guys did their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有没有完成水泥固井测验\N{\fs14}Did they run the cement log?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\fs14}Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 先生 你是不是没有跟我提起\N{\fs14}Thank you. Gentlemen, you couldn't perhaps enlighten me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,水泥固井测验的事情 啊\N{\fs14}on this cement log situation, could ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 水泥固井测验 - 嗯\N{\fs14}- Cement log? - Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们有没有打算做 有没有\N{\fs14}Do you know if they're planning it? Running it? Did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃 - 嗯\N{\fs14}- Mmm. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 嘿 罗尼\N{\fs14}Not really. Hey, Ronnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的福特野马可能是点火的出了点问题\N{\fs14}Might be an ignition problem with your Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在想可能是火花塞堵了\N{\fs14}I was thinking it was maybe fouled plugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能是电线 分配器的问题\N{\fs14}Well, it could be a wire. Could be distributor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能听见有规律的摩擦声吗 - 没有\N{\fs14}- Does it sound like it's skipping? - Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我能帮你什么大忙吗 姑娘\N{\fs14}You know what I'm gonna do for you, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想想你的车出的问题最多能给你带来多大损失吧\N{\fs14}Keep thinking about all the expensive things could be wrong with your ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 谢谢 - 嘿 是手动档还是自动档的\N{\fs14}- Gee, thanks. - Hey, stick shift or automatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你很熟吗\N{\fs14}Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你应该别再动你的离合器了\N{\fs14}Oh, you gotta stop grindin' shit out of that clutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦 好 丰田先生  - 哦 啊哈\N{\fs14}- Oh, yeah. Says Mr. Toyota.  - Yeah. Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,全体人员请注意\N{\fs14}Attention on the rig.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,钻井平台安全警告\N{\fs14}Rig safety announcement...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把钻工移过来\N{\fs14}Roughneck movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,过来一点 移过来一点\N{\fs14}Come to me, baby. Come to me, baby. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,清空这400桶泥浆\N{\fs14}Bleed 400 barrels of mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 开始作业\N{\fs14}Roger that. Beginning actuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我想唱\N{\fs14}Can I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,钻井乐趣多呀 乐趣多呀 乐趣多呀\N{\fs14}♪ Trippin' pipe is lots of fun lots of fun, lots of fun"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fs14}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 兄弟\N{\fs14}Hey. Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 迈克\N{\fs14}What up, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗 凯莱布 - 嘿 迈克 你好啊\N{\fs14}- How you doin', Caleb? - Hey, Mike, how you doin', man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,几个小时前 我很好\N{\fs14}I was a lot better couple hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么这么说 - 我在睡觉啊\N{\fs14}- Why's that? - I was asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗 - 是啊\N{\fs14}- Yeah? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都被叫醒了 然后又来干活\N{\fs14}We all got woken up and got us working over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果今晚要想要回去 就要努力干活了\N{\fs14}We got a lotta pipe to pull if we're gonna get out of here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不穿工服 你穿这个好看啊\N{\fs14}What's up with street clothes? You look pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟 吉米先生生气了 想要知道是否做了水泥固井测试\N{\fs14}Aw, man, Mr. Jimmy's pissed and wants to know if we got a cement bond log test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定 我觉得没做\N{\fs14}I'm not sure. I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有吗 嘿 谢恩 - 啥事\N{\fs14}- No? Hey, Shane! - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fs14}Come here, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,斯伦贝榭做了水泥胶结测井测试吗\N{\fs14}Schlumberger run a cement bond log test?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我想他们应该没有做\N{\fs14}I don't know. I don't think they did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我刚醒 - 是不是很傻\N{\fs14}- I just woke up, so... - Is that stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道是不是很傻 但是\N{\fs14}I don't know if it's stupid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也不聪明 - 也不聪明\N{\fs14}- It ain't smart. - It ain't smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你们 像是花样游泳运动员\N{\fs14}Look at you guys. Like synchronized swimmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你们是想太多了 脑袋疼\N{\fs14}I think you think too much, you gonna give him a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 快滚吧\N{\fs14}All right, get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 - 起 起 起\N{\fs14}- All right, yeah. - Up, up, up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我正看着我们的钻工\N{\fs14}Okay, I'm watchin' our roughnecks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伙计们 - 你身上这穿得啥啊\N{\fs14}- Fellas. - What the hell are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,吉米先生想要知道斯伦贝榭的队伍是否做了水泥胶结测井测试\N{\fs14}Mr. Jimmy wants to know if the team from Schlumberger ran a cement bond log test.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 固井测试\N{\fs14}- A what? - Cement job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,固井测试 拜托 跟我说说\N{\fs14}Test the cement job. Come on, man, work with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是谁来着 - 废话少说\N{\fs14}- Who's that again? - Oh, cut the shit, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜托 吉米很生气 - 斯伦贝榭 一群二货\N{\fs14}- Come on, Jimmy's pissed, man. - Schlum-burger, you democrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,到底做了测试没有\N{\fs14}Well, did we run the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 维德林 卡鲁扎没有让他们做测试就回去了\N{\fs14}No, Vidrine, Kaluza sent 'em home without testin' anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到底来做什么\N{\fs14}Why in the hell would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从不考虑我的想法 迈克\N{\fs14}They never feel the urge to take me through their thinkin', Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我确定有些事情要做\N{\fs14}But I assume it's got somethin' to do with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,赚钱 赚钱 赚钱 赚钱 赚钱\N{\fs14}♪ Money, money, money, money
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,赚钱\N{\fs14}♪ Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,电话坏了\N{\fs14}Your phones are broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 吉米先生\N{\fs14}Hey, Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你说\N{\fs14}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,英国石油公司没让斯伦贝榭团队做任何测试就送他们回去了\N{\fs14}BP sent Schlumberger team home without running any test.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没有水泥胶结测井测试结果\N{\fs14}There was no cement bond log.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 迈克\N{\fs14}Thank you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克 工作站A刚刚崩溃了\N{\fs14}Mike, "A" chair just crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死 - 又蓝屏了\N{\fs14}- Goddamn it. - Blue screen o' death again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 兄弟 你那边工作站什么情况\N{\fs14}Hey, Duck, is your chair still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我电脑屏幕在闪\N{\fs14}My computer screen is shaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我的烟雾报警器坏了\N{\fs14}And my smoke detector's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.24,0:22:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗 迈克 该死\N{\fs14}How you doin', Mike? Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我得先回去放包 拿工具 我会回来修的\N{\fs14}I'm gonna dump my bags and grab my tools and I'll be back to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,用创口贴和口香糖修修补补么\N{\fs14}Doin' it all with Band-Aids and bubble gum, my man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,每次我想成立个乐队\N{\fs14}Every time I peel off a Band-Aid on this rig,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这都能找到三 四个人\N{\fs14}I find three or four more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,费嘴皮是不行的 再来一次赚钱的那段 来啊\N{\fs14}Spit and glue ain't gettin' it done. One more time with the "money". Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 你们都练了这么久\N{\fs14}Come on, you been rehearsin' for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,赚钱 赚钱 赚钱\N{\fs14}♪ Money, money, money...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.11,0:22:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 来高潮\N{\fs14}No, no, the good part, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是高潮了 赚钱\N{\fs14}That is the good part!? Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,人为财死\N{\fs14}♪ I'd kill for that money
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,全是美元\N{\fs14}♪ Almighty dollar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 好莱坞\N{\fs14}Hi, Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 迈克 - 什么事 戴尔\N{\fs14}- Hey, Mike! - What's the word, Dale?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:22:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,完事儿了吗\N{\fs14}What do you know? We done?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还没 快了\N{\fs14}Not much. Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚打算偷偷钓鱼\N{\fs14}Yeah, I'm going fishing tonight. Undercover.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们今晚就会离开这个井了\N{\fs14}I got a feelin' we're getting off this well tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得根本没时间去钓鱼\N{\fs14}I don't think nobody's gonna be doin' no fishin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你要用你的吊车 钓个鲸鱼啥的吗\N{\fs14}You gonna use your crane, man? Maybe catch a beluga or Shamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好主意 妈的\N{\fs14}Good idea. Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌下一次我们还会在同一个位置\N{\fs14}Wanna make a bet we're at the same spot next hitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是 赔率呢 - 50比1\N{\fs14}- Yeah, give me odds. - 50-to-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的 我不赌了\N{\fs14}Ah, shit. I ain't touchin' that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 30比1 同一个位置 - 不要\N{\fs14}- 30-to-1. Same spot. - No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克 威廉姆斯 你个铁公鸡\N{\fs14}Mike Williams, you cheap bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 帕特里克 - 怎么了 迈克\N{\fs14}- Patrick. - What's goin' on, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,说啥 我听说收工了\N{\fs14}What's the word? I heard we done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.20,0:24:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你听说收工了吗 - 是啊 我听说收工了\N{\fs14}- You heard we're done? - Yeah, I heard we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁告诉你的 - 我不能跟你说 迈克\N{\fs14}- Who'd you hear that from? - I can't tell y'all that, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.80,0:24:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思 不能告诉我\N{\fs14}What do you mean, you can't tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不能告诉你 迈克\N{\fs14}I just can't tell y'all that, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.28,0:24:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么不能告诉我 - 我只是不能说而已\N{\fs14}- Why can't you tell me that? - I just can't tell ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我可以告诉你戈登在找你\N{\fs14}But I can tell ya that Gordon's lookin' for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是戈登告诉你收工了\N{\fs14}Did Gordon tell you we were done?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.72,0:24:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是 - 戈登想干嘛\N{\fs14}- No. - What does Gordon want?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.11,0:24:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 他有东西给你看\N{\fs14}I don't know. He got somethin' to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.71,0:24:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你又知道啥 - 我只知道收工了\N{\fs14}- What do you know? - I know we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.08,0:24:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你去过我的工作站了\N{\fs14}Were you in my shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是 - 别碰我的东西\N{\fs14}- No. - Don't touch my shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.79,0:24:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会碰你的东西\N{\fs14}I wasn't touchin' your shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.04,0:24:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 去整理东西吧\N{\fs14}All right, go fix something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.04,0:24:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 祝你今天顺利啊 迈克\N{\fs14}All right have a wonderful day, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.16,0:24:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你也是\N{\fs14}Yeah, you too. Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.52,0:24:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 亲爱的 等等\N{\fs14}Hold on, baby, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚说什么\N{\fs14}Shh. What were you sayin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.58,0:24:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息 完好无损\N{\fs14}Great news. Chopper didn't crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.00,0:24:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,失望了 我还打算重新嫁人\N{\fs14}Shit, I assumed and then I remarried.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.00,0:24:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 他有钱吗\N{\fs14}Oh, yeah? He rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.56,0:24:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,记得你妈妈说的\N{\fs14}Remember what your mama always said,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.95,0:24:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,费利西娅宝贝 嫁个有钱人日子总是比较好过\N{\fs14}"Just as easy to marry a rich man, Felicia, honey."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.74,0:24:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 如果每次提到我妈说的话 我都能得到1块钱\N{\fs14}Baby, if I had a nickel for all the dumb shit my mom said,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会变成一个富婆的\N{\fs14}I wouldn't need a rich man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.20,0:25:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说一句 你得修下这个 你得修下烤箱\N{\fs14}You gotta fix this by the way. You have got to fix this stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.16,0:25:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等我回家 马上修 不用担心\N{\fs14}I'm gonna fix it as soon as I get home, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 过来点儿\N{\fs14}Hey, come close to the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.72,0:25:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯哼 - 来电脑前面\N{\fs14}- Huh? - Come over to the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.48,0:25:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你的眼睛\N{\fs14}Give me those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.85,0:25:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你的工作怎么样\N{\fs14}How is it out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.08,0:25:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,日复一日 像在地狱\N{\fs14}Same shit. Well from Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.04,0:25:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你准备好了吗 - 准备\N{\fs14}- You ready? - Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.76,0:25:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 3 2 1 开始\N{\fs14}- Three... Two... - One... Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.28,0:25:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这脸蛋\N{\fs14}That face.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.76,0:25:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太帅了\N{\fs14}Sociopath.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.92,0:25:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是焦点\N{\fs14}Oh, that's... That is focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.96,0:25:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,代表决心 浓烈 冲动\N{\fs14}That is determination. That is intensity. Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.84,0:25:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你输了\N{\fs14}Ah! I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌输给你 讨厌\N{\fs14}I hate losing to you. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.75,0:25:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见\N{\fs14}I'll see you soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.66,0:25:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好 再见\N{\fs14}All right. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.24,0:25:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要碰我的东西 碰我的东西\N{\fs14}Why they touchin' my shit? Touchin' my shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.36,0:25:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,碰我的东西\N{\fs14}Touchin' my shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.64,0:25:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想让我们去下一个工作地点\N{\fs14}I can tell ya they want us to head to our next location.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.32,0:25:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,卡斯基达\N{\fs14}Kaskida.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.12,0:26:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这些你跟公司的人看过吗 卡鲁扎 维德林和那些人\N{\fs14}Was this run by anybody at BP? Kaluza, Vidrine, anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.79,0:26:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,维德林跟我确认过 这是韦德林提出来的\N{\fs14}Vidrine ran it by me. This... This comes from Vidrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.21,0:26:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍勃 让我来告诉你最重要的事情\N{\fs14}Bob, let me impose upon you what I think is most important here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.09,0:26:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须在5月16号之前从马孔多赶到卡斯基达\N{\fs14}We need to go from Macondo to Kaskida by May 16th.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.60,0:26:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,卡斯基达不同寻常的大 三十到四十亿桶\N{\fs14}Kaskida is an uncommon prospect. Three to four billion barrels?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.74,0:26:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这比公司都值钱\N{\fs14}That's worth more than BP itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.68,0:26:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你看我像圣诞老人么\N{\fs14}Do I look like fuckin' Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.20,0:26:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来是挺像圣诞老人的\N{\fs14}You do look a little like Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.24,0:26:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,迈尔斯为密西根打过球 他确实有路易斯安那的风格\N{\fs14}Coach Miles may have played in Michigan but that boy got Louisiana soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.04,0:26:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对阵萨班吗  - 是的 因为我们赢了\N{\fs14}- Versus Saban? - Hey, just 'cause we win...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.24,0:26:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说得好像你去过巴马一样\N{\fs14}Roy! Sayin' "we" like you went to Bama?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.63,0:26:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你上过路易斯安那州立大学吗\N{\fs14}Did you go to LSU?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.68,0:26:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,当我还小的时候就有人教我\N{\fs14}When I was potty trained,I was taught to flush,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.77,0:26:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,边招手边说塔斯卡卢萨县见\N{\fs14}wave and say, "See you at Tuscaloosa."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.32,0:26:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个以前在政府工作吗\N{\fs14}Hey, you boys working for the government?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.75,0:26:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,打扫卫生吗\N{\fs14}Cleaning a clean room?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.00,0:26:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在准备最后的泥浆 已经超过每平方寸5000磅压力了\N{\fs14}We're still finding mud from the last kick. Over 5,000 PSI.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.92,0:26:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拿个扫把来 - 太疯狂了\N{\fs14}- Grab a mop! - Whoo! That's just crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.60,0:26:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这次井涌造成的好事\N{\fs14}Look what the pressure did to this drill string during the kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.48,0:26:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该好好表扬下啊 - 大实话\N{\fs14}- That's one for the trophy case.- True dat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.32,0:26:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 帕特里克说你有事找我\N{\fs14}Hey, Patrick said you got somethin' for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.38,0:26:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 先生\N{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.20,0:26:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,四天前 4号页岩分离器出现故障\N{\fs14}Before y'all took off last time, shaker four goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.32,0:27:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我查了一下\N{\fs14}After some pokin' and proddin',
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.68,0:27:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,发现了问题的根源\N{\fs14}I finally found the source of the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.96,0:27:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞅瞅\N{\fs14}Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.04,0:27:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我从去年开始就一直帮你留着\N{\fs14}I been hidin' this for you since your last hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.76,0:27:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是颗牙齿吗\N{\fs14}Is that a tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好兄弟\N{\fs14}Oh, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.16,0:27:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我家小丫头一定会开心死的 谢谢\N{\fs14}You just made a little girl's year. And her old man's. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.40,0:27:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我欠你的\N{\fs14}I owe you, man. Oh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.88,0:27:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 现在开始搭建钻杆\N{\fs14}All right, boys, let's rig up the kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.88,0:27:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 戈登\N{\fs14}Hey, Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.80,0:27:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计 我要告诉你 这一定会有场大暴风雨的\N{\fs14}Hey, fellas, I'm tellin' ya, it's gonna be a full-on shit storm once Mr...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.64,0:27:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们送他们回家了 - 是啊\N{\fs14}- They sent them home. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.44,0:27:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟我走 迈克 - 我们去哪儿\N{\fs14}- Walk with me, Mike. - Where we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.60,0:27:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,去杀了BP公司的人\N{\fs14}To murder some BP company men.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.42,0:27:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 我这儿有锤子和螺丝刀 - 很好\N{\fs14}- Shit, I got hammer, screwdriver. - Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.68,0:27:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克 你早上刷牙了吗\N{\fs14}Say, Mike, did you brush your teeth this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.72,0:27:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,刷了 先生\N{\fs14}Ah, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.88,0:27:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,剔牙了吗\N{\fs14}Boy, did you floss?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.84,0:27:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 为啥\N{\fs14}Uh, no. No, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.56,0:27:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说 剔牙会让你的将来省钱又省心\N{\fs14}Save ya a lotta pain and money in the long run, I'll tell ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.76,0:27:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我擦 - 吉米要\N{\fs14}- Shit. - Jimmy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.84,0:27:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他要去找BP公司的人算账\N{\fs14}Oh, he's about to go off on the BP guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.16,0:27:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们没有做水泥测井 - 他们什么都没做\N{\fs14}- They never ran that cement log. - They didn't run nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.84,0:28:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么都没有做就让他们回家了 现在我们要去追究责任\N{\fs14}They sent 'em home without doin' shit, now we goin' after BP.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.69,0:28:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 怎么了 怎么 你欠了他们很多钱吗\N{\fs14}Hey! What's the matter? What, ya owe 'em a lotta money?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.17,0:28:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 迈克 跟我走\N{\fs14}Come on, Mike, stay on my hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.76,0:28:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死  - 去吧\N{\fs14}- Shit! - Get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.56,0:28:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好 亲爱的\N{\fs14}Yeah, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.44,0:28:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,唐 看看第51行 你会看到你的预算上限的\N{\fs14}Don, look at line 51.Your ceiling cost variances.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.48,0:28:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是让你看51行\N{\fs14}I'm not showing 51.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.05,0:28:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是维德林和卡鲁扎本人吗\N{\fs14}Well, if it isn't Don Vidrine and Bob Kaluza.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.36,0:28:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 欢迎回来 吉米先生 - 是啊\N{\fs14}- Welcome back, Mr. Jimmy. - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.24,0:28:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们放置了15立方米的水泥\N{\fs14}So, we got all 500 feet of cement poured, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.28,0:28:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs14}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.44,0:28:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,水泥固井是唯一保护我们安全的设施\N{\fs14}That cement's the only thing between us and a blowout.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.04,0:28:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 已经凝固了吗  - 是的\N{\fs14}- And it's cured? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.44,0:28:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,时间足够吗\N{\fs14}Had enough time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.76,0:28:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这事是需要花时间的\N{\fs14}Takes time to do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.12,0:28:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果水泥有问题\N{\fs14}I mean, if that cement job is compromised
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.52,0:28:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那一切都完了\N{\fs14}then everything above it is too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.00,0:28:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没事儿 休斯敦没事儿\N{\fs14}Well, it's not compromised. Houston doesn't have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.56,0:28:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想斯伦贝榭的人也是这么说的吧\N{\fs14}So I assume Schlumberger guys said the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.48,0:28:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且水泥胶结测井也是同样的结果吗\N{\fs14}Cement bond log they ran said the same, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.00,0:28:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对水泥的强度是有信心的 是吧\N{\fs14}We are confident in the integrity of our cement job, are we not?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.50,0:28:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们确实对水泥固井的生效很有信心\N{\fs14}Oh, we quite comfortable with the integrity of that cement, that for true.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.88,0:28:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就像我爷爷一样\N{\fs14}You guys are just like my granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.32,0:28:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14}Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.40,0:29:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我爷爷永远也不去看牙医\N{\fs14}Well, you see, my granddaddy, he, uh, he never even went to the dentist
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.00,0:29:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想知道他的牙出了什么问题\N{\fs14}'cause he didn't wanna know all what was wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.76,0:29:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这样他就不得不处理它\N{\fs14}'cause then he'd have to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.20,0:29:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想知道水泥到底\N{\fs14}You don't wanna know if that cement job
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.35,0:29:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是有问题 因为项目已经43天 超预算5千万了\N{\fs14}on this well is shit 'cause you're 43 days and $50 million over budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.52,0:29:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这就算有结论了吧 吉米先生\N{\fs14}You really should include yourself in that, Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.08,0:29:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,公司决定开始钻井 鲍勃 那么无论结果如何都是你的责任\N{\fs14}BP picked this spot to drill, Bob. Consequences of that's on you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.60,0:29:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我得处理这个烂摊子\N{\fs14}Of Course, I gotta try to deal with those consequences,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.04,0:29:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我在这其中\N{\fs14}so yeah, I'm included.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.24,0:29:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,重点是 他们没有做测试\N{\fs14}The point is, you sent the testing team home
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.33,0:29:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就让他们回去了\N{\fs14}before they could do their job,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.56,0:29:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为试验结果可能不让你们满意\N{\fs14}maybe give y'all some news y'all didn't wanna hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.10,0:29:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这个试验得花他们多少钱 12万5\N{\fs14}What would it have cost you to run that test, huh? 125 grand?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.16,0:29:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们公司市值1800亿啊 也太小气了\N{\fs14}You're a $180 billion company and you're cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我什么我们市值1800亿\N{\fs14}That's why we a $186 billion company.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.16,0:29:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们担心那些支出 - 我担心我的油井\N{\fs14}- We worry about those bills. - I worry about my rig.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.68,0:29:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人都住在上面 而你们只是租用\N{\fs14}My crew lives on it. You just rent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.44,0:29:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,唐 我们都知道需要停下来做维护工作\N{\fs14}Don, you and I both know we need some downtime for maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.92,0:29:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克 有多少机器需要检修了\N{\fs14}Mike, how many of our machines need repair?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.48,0:29:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 390个 吉米先生 - 390\N{\fs14}- Uh, 390, Mr. Jimmy. - Three hundred and ninety?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.32,0:29:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 差不多是全部机械的百分之十\N{\fs14}Yes, sir. Almost ten percent of all the machinery aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.72,0:29:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,举几个例子\N{\fs14}Name a few for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.20,0:29:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 几个 - 嗯\N{\fs14}- A few? - Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.88,0:30:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道有没有关键设备损坏了\N{\fs14}I would love to hear exactly what piece of mission critical equipment are down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.32,0:30:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我该从何说起呢\N{\fs14}Shit, where do I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.44,0:30:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,钻井工作站A BOP控制器 电话\N{\fs14}"A" drilling chair. Process Station 18. BOP control pods. Telephone system.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.40,0:30:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,存储 GPS天线 监控录像 互联网\N{\fs14}Pipe-racking system. GPS antenna. Direct TV system. Wireless lnternet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.00,0:30:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,卷盘 水泵 烟雾报警器\N{\fs14}Iron roughneck. Top drive rack back system.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.56,0:30:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,系统混合器 驱动管理\N{\fs14}Auxiliary draw-works control. Salt water service pumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.68,0:30:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,警报系统\N{\fs14}Smoke alarms in the galley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.40,0:30:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你会觉得热\N{\fs14}And the reason why you're sweatin' so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.69,0:30:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里的空调也坏了\N{\fs14}is 'cause the compressor for the AC on this deck are down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.56,0:30:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,只有厕所是好的吗\N{\fs14}Everything but the toilets, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.40,0:30:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 厕所也坏了\N{\fs14}No, no, you got problems there, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.64,0:30:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那不归我管 我是工程师\N{\fs14}but I don't do shitters. That's Engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.56,0:30:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哪位\N{\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.92,0:30:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克 威廉姆斯 首席工程师\N{\fs14}Mike Williams, chief ET.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.04,0:30:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我来重复一遍 我在直升机上跟那些头头们说的话\N{\fs14}I'm going tell you like I told your executives on the chopper ride in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.15,0:30:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那他们什么时候要过来呢\N{\fs14}And how 'bout the timing of that visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.68,0:30:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们来采油之前\N{\fs14}We gonna properly secure this well
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.04,0:30:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得保证平台的正常稳定\N{\fs14}before a production platform come in right after us and starts pumpin' oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.52,0:30:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸的是 这些工作需要时间\N{\fs14}Unfortunately, to do it properly takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.76,0:30:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,43天 44天\N{\fs14}43 days? 44 days?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.12,0:30:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,继续数 鲍勃\N{\fs14}Keep countin', Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.20,0:30:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,45天 46天\N{\fs14}45 days? 46 days?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.92,0:30:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 吃块饼干 鲍勃 - 噢\N{\fs14}- Have a cookie, Bob. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.64,0:31:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没有测试\N{\fs14}Can't run a cement log.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.20,0:31:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你我们接下来怎么办\N{\fs14}I'll tell you what we gonna do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.88,0:31:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先做负压力测试 然后再说其他的\N{\fs14}We gonna run the negative pressure test, before we do anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.68,0:31:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真的觉得必要的话\N{\fs14}If you really think we need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.72,0:31:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这很必要 你也应该这么想\N{\fs14}I really think we need one, Bob, and so should you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.32,0:31:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是我们现在也不知道这口井到底稳不稳定\N{\fs14}Especially since we got no idea whether this well is stable or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.96,0:31:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,接通了 好日子要来了\N{\fs14}Hey! Dial tone! Day's lookin' up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.32,0:31:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,安德森先生 我是吉米\N{\fs14}Mr. Anderson, it's Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.68,0:31:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要做负压力测试 从3000米开始\N{\fs14}We gonna run a negative pressure test. Start trippin' out 3,000 feet of pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.36,0:31:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.12,0:31:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子 不好意思\N{\fs14}Uh, young man, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.63,0:31:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你能告诉我哪里能找到迈克 威廉姆斯吗\N{\fs14}Can you tell me where I could find a Mr. Mike Williams?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.38,0:31:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 他在维修站 饭厅隔壁\N{\fs14}Yes, sir. He's in the ET shop on the second deck by the coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.29,0:31:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 今天好运 先生\N{\fs14}- Thank you much. - Have a wonderful day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.04,0:31:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是 先生\N{\fs14}And you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.28,0:31:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,威廉姆斯先生\N{\fs14}Mr. Williams?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.52,0:32:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,维德林先生 你迷路了吗\N{\fs14}Mr. Vidrine, are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.56,0:32:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.76,0:32:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只是路过来找你聊聊\N{\fs14}Just was lookin' to come by and visit with ya for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.84,0:32:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我有什么可以帮您\N{\fs14}Well, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.48,0:32:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只是感觉刚才 你还有话要说\N{\fs14}Seems as though you had something more you wanted to say in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.24,0:32:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想着给你个机会说出来\N{\fs14}And I thought I'd give you the time to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.68,0:32:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧 钻井坏了吗 - 我可没这么说\N{\fs14}- Okay, so... This rig is broke? - I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.56,0:32:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉你就是这意思\N{\fs14}Sounded like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.20,0:32:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,维德林先生你来我这到底干什么？\N{\fs14}Is there a reason you're in my shop, Mr. Vidrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.72,0:32:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们BP是一个大公司 迈克\N{\fs14}We a big company, Mike, BP.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.84,0:32:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一个复杂而庞大的组织\N{\fs14}A very big far-reaching, complex organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.69,0:32:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有无数的小部件协同工作\N{\fs14}Lot of movin' parts. Millions of movin' parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.80,0:32:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有成千上万的员工\N{\fs14}Thousands upon thousands of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.08,0:32:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们非常努力的试图保持这些人\N{\fs14}And we all work very hard to ensure that all those people
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.12,0:32:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这些部门都能正常工作\N{\fs14}and all those movin' parts are functionin' properly
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.12,0:32:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,从而得到好结果\N{\fs14}as a means to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.80,0:32:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一个可以挣钱的结果 这是宏伟的目标\N{\fs14}A very profitable end for all of us. So they the big picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.36,0:33:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也有不一样的 就像你们这些只看眼前的\N{\fs14}They the little picture, like you and the malfunctionin' shitters.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.24,0:33:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,问题在于 所有一切都是相互影响的\N{\fs14}But you see, in point of fact,they all kind of interconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.77,0:33:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,像流动的水一样 迈克\N{\fs14}They a flow at work here, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.92,0:33:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你坏了 这就坏了 然后我坏了\N{\fs14}So if you off, it's off. Then I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.36,0:33:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都坏了 整个项目就停了\N{\fs14}Then we off. Then the whole damn train is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.72,0:33:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白我的意思吗 威廉姆斯先生 - 你吃药了吗 维德森先生\N{\fs14}- You feel me, Mr. Williams? - You on medication, Mr. Vidrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.76,0:33:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在评估 我们这趟火车离脱轨还有多久\N{\fs14}I am merely tryin' to assess just how close this train is huggin' the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.92,0:33:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fs14}Okay. I hear ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.92,0:33:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想听我的意见 真的想听我的意见吗\N{\fs14}You want my take? I mean, you really want my take?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.64,0:33:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的 - 好\N{\fs14}- I do. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.84,0:33:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你们这是试图让飞机在降落的时候正好用完油\N{\fs14}I think you all tryin' to run out of fuel as the wheels touch down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.36,0:33:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,耗得一干二净不是明智之举\N{\fs14}Runnin' out of gasoline as the plane lands is not smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.36,0:33:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这有思考缺陷 这是一种侥幸\N{\fs14}It's flawed thinking. It's hope as a tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.24,0:33:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,记住了 谢谢\N{\fs14}Duly noted. And much appreciated, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.52,0:33:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这仅仅是个小员工的小意见\N{\fs14}Just the opinion of the little guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.44,0:33:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是鲶鱼吗\N{\fs14}That a catfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.32,0:34:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 65磅\N{\fs14}Yep. 65 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.96,0:34:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么钓的 用钓鱼竿吗\N{\fs14}What y'all call that? Nibblin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.40,0:34:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,手抓 直接用手抓鱼\N{\fs14}Noodlin'. We noodle for catfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.68,0:34:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的是 我们去抓鱼的时候\N{\fs14}And you know, it's funny, 'cause when we go noodlin',
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.48,0:34:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我最好的朋友皮纳特和我到湖上\N{\fs14}my best friend Peanut and I, we go down there
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.28,0:34:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,点上灯 走到船用坡道那边去\N{\fs14}with a fifth of Crown and a lake.Walk down the boat ramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.84,0:34:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,然后找个最大最黑的洞伸手去掏\N{\fs14}We look for the biggest, darkest, blackest hole we can stick our arm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.36,0:34:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,希望这些鲶鱼能咬住我们的手\N{\fs14}And we hope one o' them big ass sons-o-bitches
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.04,0:34:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我们才能把它抓出来\N{\fs14}bites down on us as hard as he can so we can rip his ass out of that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.44,0:34:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望被咬\N{\fs14}We wanna get bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.48,0:34:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,被咬才能抓到鱼\N{\fs14}That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.68,0:34:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,区别在于 我们做好被咬的准备了\N{\fs14}Difference is, we're ready for that bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.32,0:34:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备好\N{\fs14}We are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.48,0:34:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有合适的鞋子 帽子 手套 墨镜 做好了一切准备\N{\fs14}We're wearin' shoes, hats, gloves, skullcaps, sunglasses, and we are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.52,0:34:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不会不做准备的就把手伸进去\N{\fs14}I don't stick my hand in that hole with that monster
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.95,0:34:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,祈求老天保佑\N{\fs14}and hope for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.64,0:34:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没准备的空想是不现实的 唐\N{\fs14}Uh-uh. Hope ain't a tactic, Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.12,0:34:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你抽空\N{\fs14}I thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.16,0:34:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你一天顺利 先生\N{\fs14}Have a wonderful day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.60,0:34:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是\N{\fs14}And you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.84,0:34:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,卑鄙小人\N{\fs14}Piece of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.12,0:34:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,全体注意\N{\fs14}Attention on the rig,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.40,0:34:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,负压试验即将开始\N{\fs14}negative pressure test is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.40,0:34:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,无关人员\N{\fs14}All non-essential personnel,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.97,0:35:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,请离开现场\N{\fs14}please stay clear of the rig floor, mud pits...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.28,0:35:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,顺着水流引过来\N{\fs14}Bring her into the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.56,0:35:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,右转10度 锁定176度\N{\fs14}Come right ten degrees. Lock heading at 1-7-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.08,0:35:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,右转10度\N{\fs14}Coming right ten degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.84,0:35:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,锁定176度\N{\fs14}Turning to 176.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.52,0:35:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,转向\N{\fs14}Turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.64,0:35:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,戴蒙 班克斯顿\N{\fs14}Damon B. Bankston...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.04,0:35:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的第5杯了吧？\N{\fs14}What is that, your fifth cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.88,0:35:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,随便问问\N{\fs14}I'm just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.00,0:35:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看 确认一切\N{\fs14}You go ahead and make sure everybody's up and fed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.76,0:35:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,准备就绪\N{\fs14}and ready to get after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.92,0:35:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这可能是最终测试了 - 收到\N{\fs14}- This might be the final test. - Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.16,0:35:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,又一次负压测试\N{\fs14}Another negative pressure test?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.48,0:35:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,又一次 再一次负压测试\N{\fs14}Another. Another negative pressure test.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.44,0:35:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有问题吗  - 这个井不行\N{\fs14}- Is there a problem? - We got a bad well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.40,0:35:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,油井都这样了 干这行还能指望什么\N{\fs14}They're all bad wells. We're in a tough prospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.96,0:35:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住这个 好莱坞\N{\fs14}Got that sledge, Hollywood?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.40,0:35:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了\N{\fs14}All right, we're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.40,0:35:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就位 锁定\N{\fs14}On station. Locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.36,0:35:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,锁定在176度 队长\N{\fs14}Locked at 1-7-6, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.44,0:35:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们向右转了10度\N{\fs14}We came right ten degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.76,0:35:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,已经锁定 你们可以做负压试验了\N{\fs14}We locked in. Y'all can run the negative test.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.52,0:35:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.12,0:35:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 开始吧 杰森 - 收到\N{\fs14}- Go ahead, Jason. - Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.88,0:35:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭上环形防喷器\N{\fs14}Closing the annular.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.96,0:36:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,开始进行负压测试\N{\fs14}Initiate negative pressure test.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.60,0:36:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,启动钻杆压力测试\N{\fs14}Initiate drill pipe pressure test.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.08,0:36:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你真觉得这是最后一次测试了吗\N{\fs14}You really think this is the last test?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.84,0:36:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的 我当然想啊 这可是地狱之井啊\N{\fs14}Shit. I hope so, yes. This here's the Well from Hell, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.16,0:37:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不会持续很久的\N{\fs14}Yeah, well, that ain't gonna last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.36,0:37:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这点能耐吗\N{\fs14}That's all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.48,0:37:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,进球\N{\fs14}Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.08,0:37:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,每平方英尺100磅\N{\fs14}A hundred pounds per square inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.52,0:37:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,问题不大 它倒推了一点\N{\fs14}That's okay. She's pushing back on us a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.78,0:37:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想让我们老实待着\N{\fs14}Just trying to keep us honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.32,0:37:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 唐\N{\fs14}Hey, Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.52,0:37:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你收到我上个月寄给你的那瓶红酒了吗\N{\fs14}Did you get that bottle of wine I sent ya 'bout a month ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.60,0:37:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了 谢谢 不光拿到了 我已经喝过了\N{\fs14}I did indeed. Thank you very much. I not only got it, I drank it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.88,0:38:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不错吧 - 很好喝\N{\fs14}- Pretty good, huh? - Very nice, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.72,0:38:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是瓶超级托斯卡纳 对吧 - 是吧\N{\fs14}- That's Super Tuscan, yeah? - Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.81,0:38:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 加雅  - 对吧  - 我知道你喜欢喝\N{\fs14}- "Gah-jah,"   - yeah?   - I know you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.20,0:38:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,加亚\N{\fs14}Gaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.08,0:38:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.20,0:38:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,加亚 它叫\N{\fs14}Gaja, it's called.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.48,0:38:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs14}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.28,0:38:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他们已经跑了一半了\N{\fs14}I think they're about halfway there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.88,0:38:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这些天你都喝多少咖啡了 汉克\N{\fs14}How much coffee you drinking these days, Hank?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.40,0:38:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,船长 我几个月前就戒了咖啡了\N{\fs14}Well, Captain, I gave it up several months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.56,0:38:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在只喝绿茶\N{\fs14}I drink nothing but green tea now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.40,0:38:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,停止摄入咖啡 每天做做瑜伽\N{\fs14}Stopped taking the coffee. Doing the yoga every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.44,0:38:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,已经坚持两周了\N{\fs14}Two weeks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.16,0:38:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,每平方英寸450磅\N{\fs14}450 PSI.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.68,0:38:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来情况不妙啊\N{\fs14}This don't look good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.64,0:39:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,压力警报\N{\fs14}Pressure warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.36,0:39:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,900\N{\fs14}Nine hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.60,0:39:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么 见鬼\N{\fs14}What the hell? Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.96,0:39:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,压力警报\N{\fs14}Pressure alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.56,0:39:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,1395磅\N{\fs14}1395.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.12,0:39:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,压力警报 压力警报\N{\fs14}Pressure alert. Pressure alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.88,0:39:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,压力警报\N{\fs14}Pressure alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.80,0:39:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,稳定在1395磅了 吉米先生 压力很大\N{\fs14}We're holding at 1395, Mr. Jimmy. That's a lot of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.92,0:39:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 足以将你的车劈开两半了\N{\fs14}Yeah. Enough to cut your car in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.04,0:39:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,打开上环形防喷器\N{\fs14}Opening the upper annular.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.92,0:39:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好莱坞 打开钻井管道阀门 我们得释放些压力\N{\fs14}Hollywood, open up the drill pipe valve. We gotta bleed pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.96,0:39:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,同志们 我不得不说 试验结果真的不行\N{\fs14}Gentlemen, I hate to say this,but that is a bad test.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.28,0:39:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也不一定 - 唐 一个好的测试应该\N{\fs14}- Not necessarily. - Oh, Don. A good test starts...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.28,0:40:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,从0开始 保持在0 到0结束\N{\fs14}Starts at zero. Stays at zero. Ends at zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.04,0:40:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 好吧 是有压力\N{\fs14}Thank you. So there was pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.64,0:40:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没看到有泥浆从管道里溢出来\N{\fs14}But there was no mud flowing up and outta that pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.84,0:40:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以解释这是为什么吗\N{\fs14}Now explain that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.56,0:40:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我承认 这是挺奇怪的\N{\fs14}That's a confusing result, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.75,0:40:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,卡鲁扎和我已经多次讨论过关于钻井管道的事\N{\fs14}Kaluza and I have talked about this drill pipe,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.08,0:40:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我们脸都气绿了\N{\fs14}until we blue in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.48,0:40:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是有些地方不是很明白\N{\fs14}There's something off with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.24,0:40:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他管这叫膀胱效应\N{\fs14}He says it's a bladder effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.72,0:40:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,膀胱效应\N{\fs14}Bladder effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.00,0:40:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,膀胱效应\N{\fs14}Bladder effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.41,0:40:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,杰森应该知道他说的是什么意思\N{\fs14}He said Jason would know what he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.88,0:40:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这上面没有显示任何溢出 对吧\N{\fs14}That one's set at no indication of flow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.31,0:40:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 看这里\N{\fs14}- Correct. - Looky here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.16,0:40:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 别擦那些我们还需要的\N{\fs14}Hey! We actually needed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.64,0:40:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,膀胱效应\N{\fs14}Bladder effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.84,0:40:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这有一团压力\N{\fs14}It is a pocket of pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.81,0:40:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,阻塞在防喷口附近\N{\fs14}trapped around the annular,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.32,0:40:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像是钻井管道的压力 因为它就阻塞在这附近\N{\fs14}which reads like drill pressure because it is trapped right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.86,0:40:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,恰恰就在传感器这个位置\N{\fs14}It is sitting right there on the sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.42,0:41:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这确实是个压力问题\N{\fs14}If this was a legitimate pressure issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.68,0:41:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就应该会有泥浆从这里流出\N{\fs14}then we would have mud flowing right back up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.35,0:41:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然后溢出整个钻井管道\N{\fs14}and out of that drill pipe right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.60,0:41:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们怎么才能验证这个说法\N{\fs14}Now, how we gonna test this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.00,0:41:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要再做一遍负压测试\N{\fs14}We gonna run that negative pressure test again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.40,0:41:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但这次是在压井管线进行\N{\fs14}But we gonna run it on the kill line.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.67,0:41:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是钻井管道\N{\fs14}Not on the drill pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.24,0:41:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然 问题出现在钻井管道\N{\fs14}Obviously, our problem is with that drill pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.24,0:41:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能会有压力达到1395磅每平方英寸\N{\fs14}You cannot have 1,395 pounds
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.61,0:41:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大到可以把你的车劈开两半\N{\fs14}of pressure per square inch, enough to cut your car in half,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.99,0:41:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,却不能把一丁点泥浆压出管道\N{\fs14}and not have any fluid being forced up and outta that pipe by that pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.00,0:41:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,弟兄们 你们鞋上有沾到泥浆吗 有吗\N{\fs14}Boys, you got a whole mess of drilling mud on your boots out there? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.36,0:41:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 唐\N{\fs14}Hey, Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.20,0:41:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,屋里有点热闹啊\N{\fs14}Gotten hot in the drill shack.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.12,0:41:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们遇到的问题 是钻井管的问题\N{\fs14}We have a problem with that drill pipe
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.70,0:41:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是传感器读给了我们错误的数据\N{\fs14}or with the sensor giving us a false reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.28,0:42:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,又或是其他千万个运行部件中的一个出错了\N{\fs14}Or any other of 1,000 moving parts down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.92,0:42:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要找出这个问题\N{\fs14}Now, the way we gonna find out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.32,0:42:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就要在压井管上做一次负压测试\N{\fs14}is run that negative pressure test on the kill line.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.39,0:42:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果压力是零 吉米先生\N{\fs14}And if they zero pressure, Mr. Jimmy,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.12,0:42:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那事情就一目了然了\N{\fs14}then that gonna tell us all we need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.73,0:42:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都同意了吗\N{\fs14}Are we in agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.76,0:42:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,同不同意我不知道 但是试一试也无妨\N{\fs14}I don't know about agreement, but never hurts to run a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.96,0:42:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fs14}Lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.96,0:42:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在情况怎么样了 吉米先生\N{\fs14}How we doing in here, Mr. Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.64,0:42:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,情况不错\N{\fs14}Oh, we doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.68,0:42:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 唐\N{\fs14}Aren't we, Don?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.68,0:42:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14}Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.40,0:42:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,公司的油井\N{\fs14}BP's well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.28,0:42:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.36,0:42:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,公司的石油\N{\fs14}BP's oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.80,0:42:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs14}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.32,0:42:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是受雇佣来钻井的工人而已\N{\fs14}And we just the help y'all hire to drill a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.84,0:42:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对 吉米先生\N{\fs14}You are correct, Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.00,0:42:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是工程延误了50天\N{\fs14}But we 50 days late.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.24,0:42:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,井也没钻好\N{\fs14}And the hole ain't drilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.60,0:42:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,吉米先生 厨房出了点问题\N{\fs14}Now, Mr. Jimmy, we have a issue in the galley.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.16,0:42:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 有一大群人在那里\N{\fs14}- What? - Yeah, a whole buncha people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.51,0:42:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只是点安全问题\N{\fs14}It's a safety issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.29,0:43:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不会耽误你很久的\N{\fs14}Yeah, won't take but a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.72,0:43:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是晚了43天 不是50天 简单数学题\N{\fs14}It's 43 days behind. Not 50. Simple mathematics.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.92,0:43:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,原本计划在3月8号完成的\N{\fs14}Original completion date was March 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.30,0:43:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 今天4月20号 43天 - 所以呢\N{\fs14}It's April 20th today. 43 days. - Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.04,0:43:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为像你这种只认识钱的混蛋至少数学会不错\N{\fs14}Think you money-hungry sons of bitches at least be good at math.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.68,0:43:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 先生们\N{\fs14}All right, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.36,0:43:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,继续吧 杜威\N{\fs14}Go ahead, Dewey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.52,0:43:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在压井管上进行负压测试\N{\fs14}Negative pressure test on the kill line.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.84,0:43:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,正在转换到压井管测试\N{\fs14}Switching to kill line test.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.25,0:43:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,启动压井管压力测试\N{\fs14}Initiating kill line pressure test.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.90,0:43:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,膀胱效应\N{\fs14}Bladder effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.04,0:43:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他的话可信吗\N{\fs14}That ring true to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.01,0:43:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然唐 维德森这人平时\N{\fs14}Well, nothing ever come outta Don Vidrine's mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.98,0:43:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,满嘴跑火车 但我觉得还行\N{\fs14}ever really rang true to me, but, yeah, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.75,0:43:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来像是真的\N{\fs14}On its face? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.98,0:43:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的话是有逻辑的\N{\fs14}There's a logic to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.33,0:43:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有点道理 但是呢\N{\fs14}It's got merit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.16,0:43:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 给压井管做压力测试\N{\fs14}I don't know, applied to drill pipes and kill lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.84,0:43:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说有点太高深了\N{\fs14}It's a little above my pay grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.20,0:43:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,应该会看到泥浆才对\N{\fs14}We should've seen some mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.76,0:44:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,压力警报\N{\fs14}Pressure warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.92,0:44:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吉米先生\N{\fs14}Mr. Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.00,0:44:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 吉米先生 - 干得好\N{\fs14}- Hey! Yeah, Mr. Jimmy! - Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.24,0:44:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,深水地平线获得公司授予的最高级别的安全表彰\N{\fs14}Deepwater Horizon is receiving BP's highest safety award
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.38,0:44:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,已连续7年\N{\fs14}for the seventh straight year.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.03,0:44:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都从吉米先生接手的时候开始\N{\fs14}And it all starts at the top with the man you call "Mr. Jimmy."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.32,0:44:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 吉米先生 吉米 - 请致辞\N{\fs14}- Mr. Jimmy, Mr. Jimmy... - Speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.37,0:45:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,稳定在0 头儿 测试结果良好 没有残留压力\N{\fs14}Held at zero, boss. It's a good test. No pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.96,0:45:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜 测试通过了\N{\fs14}Congratulations. Good test.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.20,0:45:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,钻井管里面还有1400磅每平方英寸的压力\N{\fs14}We still got 1,400 PSI on the drill line.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.72,0:45:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,钻井管和压井管的示数必须是一致的才对\N{\fs14}Drill line and the kill line should be exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.08,0:45:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,数据应该是相等的\N{\fs14}They should be all lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.35,0:45:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道是钻井管道里面出现了问题\N{\fs14}We already agreed that there's something wrong with the drill line.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.32,0:45:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你还要纠结这个\N{\fs14}So why do you keep comin' back to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.92,0:45:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道 经验之谈\N{\fs14}I don't know. Good oil field practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.76,0:45:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有泥浆 没有涌流 我们一定要开始了\N{\fs14}No mud. No flow. We got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.60,0:45:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,最快要多久才能把井门封锁好\N{\fs14}Now, how quick can we lock the door on this well?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.48,0:45:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不征得吉米先生的同意 我什么也不会做\N{\fs14}I'm not doin' nothin' until Mr. Jimmy's made aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.25,0:45:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这儿就没个有主见的成年人吗\N{\fs14}Is there a man among you? Is there an adult here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.56,0:46:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都穿得人模狗样的\N{\fs14}You all got the paraphernalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.16,0:46:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,工作服 工作鞋一穿\N{\fs14}The dip. The steel toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.83,0:46:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但都是扯淡 压井管里一点压力也没有\N{\fs14}But it's all bullshit. We got zero pressure on the kill line.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.24,0:46:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还紧张的要命\N{\fs14}You nervous as cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.52,0:46:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,动不动就干脆缩手不干\N{\fs14}Afraid to make it work at every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.08,0:46:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等我回到伦敦我就会这么汇报给我的上司\N{\fs14}That will be my summary back to my bosses in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.60,0:46:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 鲍勃 - 好吗\N{\fs14}- Bob? - Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.52,0:46:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,行 你通知吉米先生吧\N{\fs14}Again, you can call Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.52,0:46:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不耽误你们吃冰淇淋了 谢谢\N{\fs14}And don't let me keep ya from your ice cream for another second. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.20,0:46:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是吉米先生\N{\fs14}It's Mr. Jimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.36,0:46:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,负压测试完成了\N{\fs14}Ran the negative test.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.00,0:46:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,测试结果良好 没有发现压力\N{\fs14}It was a good test. We got no pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.52,0:46:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,准备撤离开始作业了 正等你点头\N{\fs14}'Bout to start displacing. Wanted your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.84,0:46:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗 詹森\N{\fs14}You sure about this, Jason?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.96,0:46:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,压井管线是完好的 我只能确定这个\N{\fs14}Kill line was good. Sure of that. That's the only thing I'm sure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.24,0:46:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人一直在催我 你想我怎么做\N{\fs14}These guys are all over me. What do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.56,0:46:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有泥浆 对不对  - 对 没有泥浆\N{\fs14}- Zero flow, correct?  - That's correct. No flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.72,0:47:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们开工了\N{\fs14}We good?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.52,0:47:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧 今晚估计是一个不眠夜了\N{\fs14}Well, looks like it's gonna be a long night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.74,0:47:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,詹森 你先在上面守着 半小时后我去找你\N{\fs14}You stay on top of it, Jason. I'll see you in about a half hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.44,0:47:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.08,0:47:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 弟兄们 测试通过了\N{\fs14}Okay, guys, good test.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.43,0:47:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶\N{\fs14}Yahoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.44,0:47:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,准备接着抽出1000桶泥浆\N{\fs14}Get ready to pull out 10,000 barrels of mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.90,0:47:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,夜班前\N{\fs14}I think I'm goin' take a shower and wash my day off
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.08,0:47:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我得洗个澡\N{\fs14}before I start my night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.68,0:47:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 漫漫长夜 是吧 - 去吃点冰激凌吧 麦克\N{\fs14}- Gonna be a long one, huh? - Get some ice cream, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.80,0:47:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我得时刻保持体形\N{\fs14}I gotta watch my figure.
