Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.00,0:55:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当\N{\fs14}Adam!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.68,0:55:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得撤了 哥们儿\N{\fs14}We gotta go, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.64,0:55:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得撤了\N{\fs14}We gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.44,0:55:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得去泥浆池那 迦勒\N{\fs14}We gotta get to the mud pit! Caleb!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.76,0:55:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,迦勒\N{\fs14}Caleb!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.92,0:55:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,走 快走\N{\fs14}Get off the floor! Get off the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.87,0:55:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是2号泵 关掉它 关掉它\N{\fs14}It's Pump 2! Bleed it! Bleed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.44,0:56:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伽勒 关闭阀门 - 引导所有的泥浆\N{\fs14}- Caleb, close the drill pipe valve - Feed the standpipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.36,0:56:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,到上层管道去\N{\fs14}Divert everything overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.53,0:56:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,杰森 我们该怎么办\N{\fs14}Jason, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.86,0:56:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有碎片砸过来了 天哪\N{\fs14}We got debris! Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.52,0:56:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 伽勒 快撤离\N{\fs14}Oh shit! Caleb, clear the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.01,0:56:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.84,0:56:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,警报没响\N{\fs14}The alarm didn't sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.21,0:56:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去看看是不是每个人都疏散出来了 你自己去救生船那儿\N{\fs14}I'm gonna make sure everyone evacuates. You get to the lifeboats.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.95,0:56:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快去 - 好的\N{\fs14}- Go! - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.28,0:56:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利 停船\N{\fs14}Halt.Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.84,0:57:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 小心\N{\fs14}Look out! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.52,0:57:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住它 快抓住它\N{\fs14}Get that! Get it! Get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.56,0:57:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么情况 - 妈的\N{\fs14}- What the heck? - Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.20,0:57:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊\N{\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.48,0:57:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,深水地平线 这里是达蒙班克斯顿号 收到请回答\N{\fs14}Deepwater Horizon, this is Damon Bankston. Copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.36,0:57:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,防喷器没有响应\N{\fs14}The BOP's not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.88,0:57:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 杜克 关闭管道 - 好的\N{\fs14}- Duck, cut the pipe! - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.24,0:57:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs14}Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.88,0:57:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,警报  杜克\N{\fs14}Gas warning.. Duck! Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.36,0:57:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 发生了什么\N{\fs14}What happened? Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.20,0:57:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,基思\N{\fs14}Keith!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.76,0:57:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,戈登\N{\fs14}Gordie!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.84,0:57:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快点 起来 - 罗伊 快点 快点啊\N{\fs14}- Come on, man! Get up! - Roy! Come on, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.20,0:57:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得走了 我们必须马上走\N{\fs14}We gotta go! We gotta go right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.92,0:58:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,燃气警报\N{\fs14}Gas warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.48,0:58:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 燃气警报响了\N{\fs14}Oh, shit. We got a gas alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.24,0:58:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,推进器转速过载\N{\fs14}Thrusters are over-revving.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.68,0:58:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这个推进器正在失去控制\N{\fs14}My thrusters are running away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.96,0:58:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我没办法让钻井保持在原位不动\N{\fs14}I'm not gonna be able to hold the rig in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.44,0:58:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 冷静\N{\fs14}All right. Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.12,0:58:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊\N{\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.88,0:58:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的错觉 还是你那边忽然闪了一下\N{\fs14}Is it just me or it just get real bright in there all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.00,0:59:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,红色\N{\fs14}Magenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.12,0:59:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,红色警报\N{\fs14}Magenta alarms!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.35,0:59:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,燃气警报响了\N{\fs14}Gas warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.96,0:59:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 油井要爆炸了 - 什么\N{\fs14}- The well is blowing out. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.13,0:59:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克\N{\fs14}Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.25,0:59:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,求救 这里是深水地平线 我们\N{\fs14}Mayday! This is Deepwater Horizon. We are in a...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.77,0:59:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在干嘛 我让你求救了么\N{\fs14}What the hell are you doing? Did I ask you to call a Mayday?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.56,0:59:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我待会儿给你回电话 一会儿打给你\N{\fs14}I'll call you back, I'll call you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.72,0:59:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你能分清是电流不稳还是爆炸吗\N{\fs14}You don't know the difference between a kick and a goddamn blowout!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.16,0:59:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那为什么  - 你毛都不懂\N{\fs14}- Why's the... - You don't know shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.76,0:59:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么屏幕上什么都没了\N{\fs14}Why's the monitor out?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.64,0:59:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,燃气警报\N{\fs14}Gas warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.48,0:59:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,求救 求救 求救 这里是深水地平线\N{\fs14}Mayday! Mayday! Mayday! This is Deepwater Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.48,0:59:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住  杜克 我会救你出去的\N{\fs14}Hang on, Duck. I'm gonna get you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.80,1:00:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天 杜威 史蒂夫\N{\fs14}God damn it! Dewey! Steve!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.44,1:00:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下 天哪\N{\fs14}Down! Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.24,1:00:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,求救 求救 求救\N{\fs14}Mayday! Mayday! Mayday!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.36,1:00:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这里是深水地平线 - 我们的钻井着火了\N{\fs14}- This is Deepwater Horizon. - Rig's on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.08,1:00:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这发生了大爆炸\N{\fs14}We've had a major explosion.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.48,1:00:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们需要救援 - 你看到那儿着火了么\N{\fs14}- We need assistance... - Can't you see it's on fire?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.24,1:00:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我再说一遍 我们这儿发生了事故性爆炸\N{\fs14}I repeat, we've had a mass casualty explosion.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.64,1:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要立即救援\N{\fs14}We need assistance immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.12,1:00:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,求救 求救 求救\N{\fs14}Mayday! Mayday! Mayday!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.72,1:01:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是深水地平线\N{\fs14}This is Deepwater Horizon...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.12,1:01:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是内燃机船达蒙班克斯顿号\N{\fs14}This is motor vessel Damon Bankston.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.96,1:01:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,深水地平线起火了\N{\fs14}Deepwater Horizon has exploded and is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.42,1:01:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,重复 深水地平线起火了\N{\fs14}I say again, the Deepwater Horizon has exploded and is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.24,1:01:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看到了巨大的爆炸\N{\fs14}We just saw a huge explosion.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.68,1:01:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 先生 深水地平线着火了\N{\fs14}Yes sir, we see the Deepwater Horizon on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.92,1:01:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 所有人都从钻井撤离了吗\N{\fs14}Okay. And everybody's off the rig?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.43,1:01:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚\N{\fs14}We have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.56,1:01:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,美国海岸警卫队指挥中心\N{\fs14}United States Coast Guard District 8 Command Center,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.24,1:01:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是少尉 范 胡纳\N{\fs14}Ensign Von Huene speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.68,1:01:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 有一个钻井台着火了\N{\fs14}Yes, there's an oil rig on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.52,1:01:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大概在离威尼斯48海里的地方\N{\fs14}About 48 nautical miles south of Venice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.76,1:01:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 有一个钻井台着火了 位置是大概在离威尼斯48海里的地方 对吗\N{\fs14}Okay, an oil rig on fire. About 48 nautical miles south of Venice?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.30,1:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我还从来没见过这样的\N{\fs14}Yes, ma'am. I've never seen anything like it...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.48,1:01:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 先生 你在哪艘船上\N{\fs14}Okay, yes, sir. What vessel are you on?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.80,1:01:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你所在的船的名字是什么\N{\fs14}What's the name of your vessel?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.48,1:01:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是美国海岸警卫队指挥中心 我是中尉德根\N{\fs14}Coast Guard District 8 Command Center, this is Lieutenant Degan speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.84,1:01:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你说有一个钻井台着火了对吗 你知道那里的地址吗\N{\fs14}An oil rig on fire? Sir, do you have a position for that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.00,1:01:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是很清楚\N{\fs14}Sir, I'm not exactly sure,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.52,1:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我得先从你那知道一点信息\N{\fs14}I need to get some information from you first.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.04,1:01:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这些了么 方便告诉我你的名字吗\N{\fs14}If that's all right. Can you give me your name, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.09,1:01:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 先生 你的位置在哪呢\N{\fs14}Okay, sir, what is your location?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.40,1:01:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我接到的是有一艘离佛琼港南面100英里的地方的船报警说看到有地方失火\N{\fs14}We got 100 miles south of Port Fourchon there's a vessel reporting a fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.74,1:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你的呢\N{\fs14}Where's your call?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.44,1:02:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,离威尼斯48海里的地方\N{\fs14}Forty-eight nautical miles south of Venice.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.16,1:02:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我这有一个来自海洋观测船的报警\N{\fs14}I had a report from a OSV.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.84,1:02:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个坐标系地址 这是一个很确切的地址\N{\fs14}That's the lat/long. That's a confirmed position.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.40,1:02:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  我们这儿有一个现场的卫星图像\N{\fs14}Sir, we got a satellite image of the scene.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.88,1:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这\N{\fs14}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.64,1:02:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.32,1:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙 听着 我们得速战速决 知道吗\N{\fs14}Listen, guys, we need to bump this up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.16,1:02:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,打给地勤部门 看看我们在那一片有些什么快艇\N{\fs14}Call land area. See what kinda float cutters we have in the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.89,1:02:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧开到现场去\N{\fs14}Divert 'em over to the area.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.92,1:02:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,空勤部 我要知道我们目前有多少飞机可以用\N{\fs14}Air stations. I need to know how many bravo aircraft we have up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.56,1:02:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 让他们都赶过去\N{\fs14}Okay, get 'em goin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.08,1:02:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fs14}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.16,1:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,疏散程序正在启动\N{\fs14}Evacuation procedure in effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.96,1:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,原来这不是演练\N{\fs14}This is not a drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.52,1:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,疏散程序正在启动\N{\fs14}Evacuation procedure in effect...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.07,1:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,道基\N{\fs14}Dougie?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.06,1:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,道基 嗨 道基 你能听到我说话么\N{\fs14}Dougie? Hey, Dougie, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.99,1:04:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说什么  - 你能听到我说话么 道基\N{\fs14}- What? - Can you hear me, Dougie?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.36,1:04:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟\N{\fs14}My little brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.72,1:04:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.44,1:04:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是他的生日\N{\fs14}It's his birthday.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.16,1:04:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我弟\N{\fs14}My little brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.36,1:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你弟没在这\N{\fs14}Your little brother's not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.56,1:04:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脚怎么样了 你能走么\N{\fs14}What about your legs? Huh? Can you move 'em?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.80,1:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我弟  - 看着我 道基\N{\fs14}- My little brother.  - Look at me, Dougie.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.00,1:04:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你得走两步 我们要走到救生船那儿去\N{\fs14}You're gonna need to use 'em. We gotta get to the lifeboats.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.40,1:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我拉你起来 好吗\N{\fs14}I'm gonna get you up. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.12,1:04:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.52,1:04:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.64,1:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,疏散程序正在启动\N{\fs14}Evacuation procedure in effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.18,1:04:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.47,1:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\fs14}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.96,1:05:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,2号推进器失灵\N{\fs14}Thruster 2 failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.36,1:05:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,左舷的四个推进器都失灵了\N{\fs14}I just lost four thrusters on the port side.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.32,1:05:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,船长 只剩下4个了\N{\fs14}I only have four left, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.60,1:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们该怎么办  - 我需要损坏报告\N{\fs14}- What do we do? - I need a damage report.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.72,1:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要手动操控钻井了\N{\fs14}I'm gonna take manual control over the rig.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.34,1:05:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是库赫达 我需要损坏报告\N{\fs14}This is Kuchta on the bridge. I need a damage report.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.60,1:05:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一定要行啊  - 火警队在哪 快点\N{\fs14}- Come on, baby. -  Where's the fire team? Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.52,1:05:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是达蒙班克斯顿 请接海岸警卫队\N{\fs14}This is Damon Bankston to Coast Guard Rescue.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.68,1:05:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在深水地平线钻井台发生了一起事故\N{\fs14}We have an incident on the Deepwater Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.84,1:05:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,带上90度软梯 救生船已经放下去了吧\N{\fs14}Bring her 'round 90 degrees starboard. Tell me that rescue boat's in the water!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.68,1:05:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 我们需要医疗器材\N{\fs14}Let's go! We need medical kits!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.64,1:05:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 氧气罩在哪 - 清空供给室 行动\N{\fs14}- Where's the oxygen tanks? - Empty out the supply house! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.16,1:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去码头\N{\fs14}Go portside!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.24,1:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,去你指定的救生船那儿\N{\fs14}Proceed to your assigned lifeboat.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.52,1:06:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fs14}Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.81,1:06:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿\N{\fs14}Hey! Hey!
