Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.12,1:24:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 我们快点上去\N{\fs14}Come on! We gotta get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.95,1:24:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.20,1:24:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在楼梯上 正往上走\N{\fs14}On the stairs, goin' high.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.44,1:24:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\fs14}Ah! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.69,1:24:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.44,1:24:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\N{\fs14}Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.49,1:25:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,加油\N{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.52,1:25:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,原始V8 还是 新一代的\N{\fs14}The original V8 or a crate motor?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.80,1:25:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 你的野马汽车\N{\fs14}- Huh? - Your Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.04,1:25:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 原始的还是新一代的引擎 - 是原始 原始的\N{\fs14}- Original V8 or crate motor? - It's original. Original.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.72,1:25:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒\N{\fs14}That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.51,1:25:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们或许要重新造一个了\N{\fs14}It, we might need to rebuild it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.52,1:25:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是谁\N{\fs14}Who's "we"?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.48,1:25:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这里还有谁\N{\fs14}You see anyone else here? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.32,1:25:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我呀\N{\fs14}Me and you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.73,1:25:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在听我说 看着我\N{\fs14}Now listen to me. Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.32,1:25:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们站的越高 跳的越远\N{\fs14}We came up higher\N{\fs14}so we can jump out further.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.87,1:25:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗 我们要跳过火海\N{\fs14}Okay? We're gonna jump over the fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.57,1:25:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.12,1:25:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\fs14}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.79,1:25:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,做不到什么 重新造个引擎\N{\fs14}Can't what? Rebuild an engine?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.52,1:25:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,跳下去\N{\fs14}Jump.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.83,1:25:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fs14}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.84,1:25:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会跳到火上 你听到了吗\N{\fs14}We're not gonna hit the fire, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.38,1:25:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不想死 - 你死不了的\N{\fs14}- I don't wanna die. - You're not gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.36,1:25:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看着我 - 我不想死\N{\fs14}- Look at me. - I don't wanna die.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.58,1:25:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不想死 - 我们的选择\N{\fs14}- I don't wanna die. - Our choice...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.84,1:25:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死\N{\fs14}I don't wanna die.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.72,1:25:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要么选择被烧死 要么选择跳下去\N{\fs14}Our choice right now is to burn or jump.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.19,1:25:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 你放开我 - 好的\N{\fs14}- No, you let go of me! - Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.43,1:25:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我 别碰我 别碰我\N{\fs14}Don't touch me!Don't touch me. Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.52,1:25:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你跳吧 - 好的\N{\fs14}- You jump. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.80,1:26:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要跳你跳吧\N{\fs14}Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.12,1:26:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 你做什么我就做什么\N{\fs14}You know what? I'ma do whatever you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.45,1:26:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我老婆叫费利西亚\N{\fs14}My wife's name is Felicia.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.60,1:26:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我女儿叫辛迪 - 不要逼我\N{\fs14}- And my daughter's Sydney. - Don't put that on me!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.12,1:26:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要见到她们 你懂了吗\N{\fs14}And I will see them again.\N{\fs14}Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.80,1:26:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你活着离开钻台的概率有多大\N{\fs14}What do you think the odds of you gettin' off this rig alive are?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.88,1:26:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不和我现在跳下去的话\N{\fs14}If you don't jump with me right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.92,1:26:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我就跳下去了 你听到了吗\N{\fs14}I'm gettin' off this rig. You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.48,1:26:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你想待在这儿\N{\fs14}You wanna stay here?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.29,1:26:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就待这儿吧\N{\fs14}You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.04,1:26:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你野马是什么颜色的\N{\fs14}Hey, what color's the Mustang?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.68,1:26:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,跳吧\N{\fs14}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.96,1:27:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,安德里亚\N{\fs14}Andrea!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.80,1:28:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,听到名字的 答一声到\N{\fs14}If you hear your name, call out!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.04,1:28:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔伯斯 尚恩 - 在\N{\fs14}- Albers Shane! -  Here!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.96,1:28:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,霍洛韦迦勒\N{\fs14}Holloway Caleb!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.28,1:28:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在\N{\fs14}Here!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.88,1:28:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,安德里亚 杰森\N{\fs14}Anderson, Jason!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.72,1:28:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,杰森 安德里亚 在吗\N{\fs14}Jason Anderson, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.04,1:28:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿有人在钻井车间工作的吗\N{\fs14}Is there anybody here from the drill shack?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.08,1:28:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没人吗\N{\fs14}Nobody?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.68,1:29:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,唐纳德 克拉克 在不在\N{\fs14}Donald Clark, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.76,1:29:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,杜威 芮维特\N{\fs14}Dewey Revette?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.48,1:29:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,尚恩 罗士托\N{\fs14}Shane Roshto?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.00,1:29:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,亚当 维斯\N{\fs14}Adam Weise?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.96,1:29:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊 肯普\N{\fs14}Roy Kemp?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.36,1:29:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,医生就在顶层 好吗\N{\fs14}We got a medic right up top, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.96,1:29:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,戴尔 巴肯\N{\fs14}Dale Burkeen?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.66,1:29:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,戈登 琼斯\N{\fs14}Gordon Jones?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.99,1:29:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔 克莱平\N{\fs14}Karl Kleppinger?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.96,1:29:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬 柯蒂斯\N{\fs14}Stephen Curtis?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.68,1:30:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,基思曼 努埃尔\N{\fs14}Keith Manuel.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.28,1:30:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.41,1:30:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.56,1:31:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都跪下来\N{\fs14}Everybody take a knee.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.88,1:31:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在天上的父 愿人都尊你的名为圣\N{\fs14}Our Father who art in heaven, hallowed be Thy name.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.84,1:31:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,愿你的国降临 愿你的旨意行在地上 如同行在天上\N{\fs14}Thy will be done on Earth as it is in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.20,1:31:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们日用的饮食 今日赐给我们\N{\fs14}Give us this day, our daily bread.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.84,1:31:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,免我们的债\N{\fs14}Forgive us our trespasses,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.72,1:31:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如同我们免了人的债\N{\fs14}as we forgive those who trespass against us.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.92,1:31:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不叫我们遇见试探 救我们脱离凶恶\N{\fs14}And lead us not into temptation, but deliver us from evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.05,1:31:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字 先生\N{\fs14}What's your name, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.16,1:31:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克 威廉姆斯\N{\fs14}Mike Williams.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.60,1:32:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  你去休息吧\N{\fs14}All right, you just need to get some rest,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.92,1:32:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,当你休息好了之后 我再找你谈话\N{\fs14}and when you do, after you're done,you'll talk to me and...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.92,1:32:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你是在钻台上的吗\N{\fs14}Hey, hey, hey. Were you on the rig?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.52,1:32:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 先生 - 我儿子有没有和你一起下来\N{\fs14}- Yes, sir.- My son get off the rig with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.80,1:32:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 钻台 - 他到底下来了没有\N{\fs14}- Rig? - Did he get off the rig?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.16,1:32:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他是否活着回来了\N{\fs14}I don't know if he made it off...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.36,1:32:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子在哪儿\N{\fs14}Where is my son?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.84,1:32:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪儿\N{\fs14}Where is my son?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.04,1:32:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他活着下来没 - 我不知道\N{\fs14}- Did he get off the rig? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.84,1:32:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子\N{\fs14}My son.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.36,1:32:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识他吗 他到底下来没呀\N{\fs14}Do you know him? Did he get off with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.00,1:32:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,最好有人出来解释清楚\N{\fs14}Somebody better tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.52,1:32:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来帮我一下\N{\fs14}Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.20,1:32:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,求你们了\N{\fs14}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.28,1:32:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,会触发一个警报\N{\fs14}...will trigger an alarm.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.52,1:32:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否听到其中任何一个警报\N{\fs14}Did you hear any one of those alarms?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.52,1:33:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 没事的\N{\fs14}Baby, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.24,1:35:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起来我闭上我的双眼 然后开始祈祷\N{\fs14}I remember closing my eyes and,and saying a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.14,1:35:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,祈祷上帝告诉我的老婆和女儿\N{\fs14}Asking God to tell my wife and little girl
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.33,1:35:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸已经竭尽全力了\N{\fs14}that, uh, Daddy did everything he could.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.55,1:35:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能够幸存下来的话 这一定是天意\N{\fs14}And if I survive this, it's for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.88,1:35:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请举起你的右手 先生\N{\fs14}Please raise your right hand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.00,1:35:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否能够郑重起誓\N{\fs14}Do you solemnly swear
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.17,1:35:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你将陈述的事情\N{\fs14}that the testimony you're about to give is the truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.50,1:35:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是千真万确 不带半点虚言的吗\N{\fs14}the whole truth and nothing but the truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.06,1:35:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 上帝可鉴  - 是的 先生\N{\fs14}- so help you God? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.28,1:35:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 先生\N{\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.04,1:35:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我去到下一个亮光出 我们在水里看到一个人\N{\fs14}We went to the next light that we saw in the water
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.00,1:36:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,并把她救了上来\N{\fs14}and retrieved that person,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.34,1:36:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是安德里亚 动态位置操作员\N{\fs14}who was Andrea,the dynamic position operator.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.20,1:36:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我到了扩音器边上并做了最后一个声明\N{\fs14}I went over to the PA and made the last announcement
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.99,1:36:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我说我们要逃离钻台了\N{\fs14}and said that we were abandoning the rig.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.24,1:36:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的记忆里 谁管理者钻台\N{\fs14}Who, in your view, was in charge of the rig?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.01,1:36:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,海上装置经理\N{\fs14}The OIM.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.92,1:36:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是哈勒尔先生\N{\fs14}And that would be Mr. Harrell.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.16,1:36:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对吗 - 对\N{\fs14}- Is that correct?\N{\fs14}- Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.31,1:36:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了一场大爆炸\N{\fs14}There was a major explosion
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.00,1:36:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,接着在右舷侧又发生了一场爆炸\N{\fs14}followed by a second explosion on the starboard side.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.72,1:36:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸过后 我给钻台打电话\N{\fs14}So after explosion, I call the rig floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.27,1:36:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没有回应\N{\fs14}No answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.56,1:36:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些\N{\fs14}All the things that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.64,1:36:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们所谓不可能发生的事情 发生了\N{\fs14}they told us could never happen happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.81,1:36:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,人们付出了生命的代价\N{\fs14}Men lost their lives.

